title: Which is the fastest 5G processor? - Quora

response.answer_text: I think that Apple’s A13 Bionic Chip is not 5g enabled. So According to me, the Qualcomm Snapdragon 865 5G is really a SuperFast And efficient processor. It has the X55 5G modem which makes it future ready. The performance would be just awesome and I think that it can stand against the A13 (Which is of course not 5g enabled). Oneplus 8 series, realme x50 pro, iqoo 3 are some smartphones with this processor
